        "# =====================================================\n",
        "# 4. Define risk prediction feature set\n",
        "# =====================================================\n",
        "# Risk prediction uses a richer feature set to improve supervised model performance.\n",
        "# Tree-based models are less sensitive to multicollinearity, so we keep more business signals here.\n",
